Package: similR
Type: Package
Title: Local Recommendation of Institutional Scientific Literature
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Henry",
      family = "Osorto",
      email = "henry.osorto@unitec.edu.hn",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides a local Shiny application and reproducible data pipeline
    for recommending institutional scientific literature. The package imports,
    cleans, deduplicates, versions, validates, and stores bibliographic records
    in DuckDB databases distributed through GitHub Releases. Recommendation
    engines are designed to operate locally and to support both lexical and
    semantic similarity in subsequent development phases.
